6
00:00:17.916 --> 00:00:20.356 A:middle
This is the Introduction
to the Photos Frameworks,

7
00:00:20.426 --> 00:00:22.206 A:middle
collectively known as PhotoKit.

8
00:00:23.156 --> 00:00:24.846 A:middle
And my name is Adam Swift.

9
00:00:25.146 --> 00:00:26.106 A:middle
No jokes, please.

10
